OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1776369950
OL,3,CNI to take on France in friendly game
OL,4,Cthis summer
OL,6,FNorthern Ireland will take on France
OL,7,Fin an international friendly this
OL,8,Fsummer, it was confirmed on Thursday.
OL,10,FThe game will take place on Monday 8
OL,11,FJune 2026 at the Decathlon Arena Stade
OL,12,FPierre-Mauroy in Lille Metropole, with
OL,13,Fa kick off time set at 21:10 local
OL,14,Ftime.
OL,16,FThe fixture will see Michael O'Neill's
OL,17,Fside come up against one of world
OL,18,Ffootball's elite nations, with France
OL,19,Fpreparing for this summer's 2026 FIFA
OL,20,FWorld Cup.
OL,26,@tD@Yrr
