OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1776369950
OL,3,CNI to take on France in friendly game
OL,4,Cthis summer
OL,6,FIt will also be Northern Ireland's
OL,7,Ffirst trip back to France almost a
OL,8,Fdecade on from the memorable UEFA Euro
OL,9,F2016 campaign.
OL,11,FThe game is the second of two away
OL,12,Ffriendly matches in June.
OL,14,FThe date, venue and opponent of the
OL,15,Ffirst game will be announced in due
OL,16,Fcourse.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/5
