PN,44603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1776369950
OL,3,CNI to take on France in friendly game
OL,4,Cthis summer
OL,6,FBoth will serve as preparations for
OL,7,Fthe UEFA Nations League campaign,
OL,8,Fwhere the team will be competing in
OL,9,FLeague B, Group B2 and face a
OL,10,Fchallenging trio of opponents:
OL,11,FHungary, Ukraine and Georgia across
OL,12,FSeptember, October and November this
OL,13,Fyear.
OL,15,FIrish FA Technical Director, Aaron
OL,16,FHughes, said:
OL,18,F"This is exactly the level of
OL,19,Fchallenge we want. France are one of
OL,20,Fthe top sides in world football so
OL,21,Fit's a great test for our players."
OL,26,@zD@AOU}D@cO]
