PN,44604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1776369950
OL,3,CNI to take on France in friendly game
OL,4,Cthis summer
OL,6,FIrish FA President, Conrad Kirkwood,
OL,7,Fsaid:
OL,9,F"This fixture marks ten years since
OL,10,FUEFA Euro 2016 when our brilliant fans
OL,11,Fcreated such special memories so it's
OL,12,Fa fitting occasion as we look forward."
OL,14,FThe last encounter between the two
OL,15,Fsides was 27 years ago when France
OL,16,Fbeat Northern Ireland by a goal to nil
OL,17,Fin Belfast.
OL,19,FAt that time, they were reigning World
OL,20,FChampions having beaten Brazil 3-0 in
OL,21,Fthe Final of the World Cup in 1998.
